      "line": 1,
      "button": "•",
      "description": "The Biker Sergeant’s bolt pistol can be replaced with one of the following:\n• 1 Astartes chainsword\n• 1 boltgun\n• 1 combi-weapon\n• 1 hand flamer\n• 1 grav-pistol\n• 1 inferno pistol\n• 1 plasma pistol\n• 1 storm bolter\n• 1 power fist\n• 1 power weapon\n• 1 thunder hammer"
    },
    {
      "datasheetId": "000000116",
      "line": 2,
      "button": "•",
      "description": "Any number of Space Marine Bikers can each have their bolt pistol replaced with 1 Astartes chainsword."
    },
    {
      "datasheetId": "000000116",
      "line": 3,
      "button": "•",
      "description": "Up to 2 Space Marine Bikers can each have their bolt pistol replaced with one of the following:\n• 1 flamer\n• 1 grav-gun\n• 1 meltagun\n• 1 plasma gun\n• 1 plasma pistol"
    },
    {
      "datasheetId": "000000116",
